<ul>
  <li>Selenium WebDriver is a browser automation framework that allows you to execute your tests against different browser.</li>
  <li>WebDriver interacts and controls the actual browser in either locally or remotely.</li>
  <li>We can use WebDriver to automate and validate Web-Applications.</li>
